    <li>Sharing links to articles on social media or private messaging</li>
    <li>Quoting short excerpts in other contexts provided you attribute the source</li>
    <li>Contacting the operator for coaching services or enquiries</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="prohibited">3. Prohibited use</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Reproducing complete articles on other sites without explicit permission</li>
    <li>Reverse engineering the site code</li>
    <li>Attempting to access non-public areas of the Site</li>
